00:06:09.040 --> 00:06:10.520
he currently holds for those salt fields—

00:06:10.520 --> 00:06:11.650
I can guarantee

00:06:11.950 --> 00:06:13.680
that once he sees them, he'll realize

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:14.600
