00:10:37.460 --> 00:10:40.470
[Contract Signatory: Gu Pingyuan]

00:10:40.550 --> 00:10:41.380
[Righteous and Diligent]

00:10:41.380 --> 00:10:43.040
The Viceroy is stepping down.

00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:45.120
The Emperor and Empress Dowager
are furious.

00:10:45.120 --> 00:10:47.050
The traitor issue is troublesome.

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:47.790
Indeed.

00:10:54.090 --> 00:10:55.600
[Righteous and Diligent]

00:10:55.600 --> 00:10:56.600
Your Excellency.

00:10:56.840 --> 00:10:58.240
No need for formalities.

00:10:58.630 --> 00:10:59.240
Everyone,

00:10:59.670 --> 00:11:00.730
as you all know,

00:11:00.870 --> 00:11:02.030
the Xianghe Trade House

00:11:02.030 --> 00:11:04.550
is planning to meddle in
the Lianghuai salt industry.

00:11:04.550 --> 00:11:07.200
I've entrusted Mr. Gu

00:11:07.270 --> 00:11:09.720
with full authority over
Liangjiang's financial and grain affairs.

00:11:09.720 --> 00:11:12.050
His orders are my orders.

00:11:12.840 --> 00:11:14.900
This matter concerns our very lives,

00:11:15.090 --> 00:11:16.750
so everyone must be cautious.

00:11:17.840 --> 00:11:18.470
Yes, Your Excellency.

